I love my Construction Master Pro, use it all the time. This calculator however is pointless. Unless you have no idea what you're doing this actually hinders material estimation. The complex estimations I would use it for are not supported and the ones that are supported are very simple and not really useful as they don't take into account real world, in the field obstacles, layouts, etc.

Functions are simple, but many building materials aren't supported.  Materials which are easy to figure out out doors for you, but complex materials aren't even supported.  No siding at all supported, quote useless if your in the trades.  Might be useful if you have no clue what you're doing...
